product_name: mophie Space Pack Battery Phone Case with 32Gb Storage - iPhone 5/5S
long_description: With 32GB of storage, the mophie Space Pack Battery Phone Case for iPhone 5/5s is the world's first battery case with built-in storage. Enjoy room for 16,000 photos, 14 hours of video and 9,000 songs.
